   Thriller series which tracks five 24-hour periods following the
   abduction of a young mother. Matt takes the kids to the fair with
   Sarah and Simone Farnes, where the grisly discovery of Leanne&#039;s body
   is made in a nearby lake. As the family reel at the news, they turn
   on each other, as the weeks of waiting take their toll. John and
   Barbara threaten to have the younger two kids taken into care. The
   police struggle to make sense of Leanne&#039;s murder, and feel they are
   no closer to finding her killer.
